# lang

JSON (RFC 8259 / TSConfig schema)

# res baseTsConfig

Shared strict TypeScript baseline that all other presets in this package extend.

Key compiler options:
- target `ES2024`, module `ESNext`, moduleResolution `Bundler`
- `strict: true`, `strictNullChecks: true`, `noUncheckedIndexedAccess: true`
- `verbatimModuleSyntax: true` — type-only imports must use `import type`
- `isolatedModules: true` — every file must be independently transpilable
- `jsx: react-jsx`, `jsxImportSource: react` — React JSX transform enabled globally
- `declaration: true`, `declarationMap: true`, `sourceMap: true`
- `noEmit: true` — emit is controlled at build time by the TSC plugin, not statically here
- `allowJs: true`, `resolveJsonModule: true`, `skipLibCheck: true`
- lib: `["DOM", "DOM.Iterable", "es2024"]`
- `incremental: false` — avoids stale build cache issues in CI
